<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Adjust tool window layout</b></p><p>Adjust the IntelliJ IDEA tool windows layout to make better use of your screen area.</p><p>Toggle between the vertical and side-by-side placement of the tool windows by pressing <span class="shortcut">Control+LeftClick</span> (on Windows and Linux) / <span class="shortcut">Control+LeftClick</span> (on macOS) on the splitter.</p></body></html>